Title: "Mechanism of Injury Value Set"
Description: "Coded concepts describing the mechanism or external cause by which an injury
was sustained (e.g., fall, motor vehicle crash, assault, stab wound, burn, drowning).
Hosted on the PGH Trauma terminology server at https://tx.fhirlab.net/fhir."
